{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_12_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 本当の私だと思ってます！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ゲーム発売後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― After the game's release",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます！　……えいっ！\nエールちゅーちゅーミラクルぽん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning! …Ei!\nAle Chu-Chu Miracle Pon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（また出合い頭に魔法がきたぞ……！？）\n（この間のことを考えると……こうだ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Another spell right as we meet…!?）\n（Considering what happened last time… take this!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれのおかげで仕事の疲れが\n全部吹き飛んだ気がするぞー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to Sumire‚ my work fatigue\nfeels like it's all blown away—?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "違いますよ、もう！　今のは時が止まる魔法です！\nこの前のとは詠唱も違うじゃないですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ seriously! That was a time-stop spell!\nThe incantation was different from last time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時が……！？　す、すまんすまん\nそれじゃ……か、かちーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Time…!? S-Sorry‚ my bad.\nThen… F-Freeze…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！　魔法が成功しました！\nこの間に{user}さんにイタズラを……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay! The magic was a success!\nI'll play a prank on {user} while he's frozen…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれ。喜んでいるところ悪いが、\nまだ魔法を習得しようとしていたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sumire. Sorry to interrupt your joy‚\nbut were you still trying to master magic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、あの時は心配させちゃってすみません\nもう大丈夫ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ sorry for worrying you back then.\nI'm okay now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら良かったよ。それにしても、すっかり魔法\n少女の役をものにしたな。演技も好評だったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad to hear that. Still‚ you've completely\nmastered the magical girl role. Your acting was well-received.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいです！　リリースされるまで不安でしたけど\nSNSでもみんな喜んでくれていて凄く安心しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so happy! I was anxious before the release‚\nbut I'm relieved everyone on SNS loved it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "私の自然体の魔法少女が見られて良かった\nという意見が多くて、頑張ったかいがありました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many said it was great to see my natural magical girl side‚\nso my hard work really paid off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "他には、私が可愛過ぎて何度もプレイした、という\n意見もありましたね。え、えへへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were also comments like‚ \"She's so cute I played it\nmultiple times.\" E-Ehehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "……お兄ちゃんがヒントを掴むきっかけをくれた\nおかげです。ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's all thanks to Big Brother giving me\nthe hint. Thank you so much!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ゲームが成功したのはすみれ達の頑張りの成果だよ\nお礼なら今度のPRイベントでファンに伝えるといい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The game's success is thanks to the hard work of everyone.\nYou should convey your thanks to the fans at the PR event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今度のPRイベントではミニライブもあるから\n他のメンバーと一緒に沢山盛り上げてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There will be a mini-live at the PR event‚\nso liven things up together with the other members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！　ゲームの成功を祝って\nみんなでミニライブをすっごく盛り上げちゃいますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! To celebrate the success‚\nwe'll totally pump up the crowd at the mini-live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――PRイベント当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Day of the PR event",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.633331867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 123.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 123.1666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "つ、ついに本番です\nちゃんとゲームの面白さとか伝えられるかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "F-Finally‚ it's the real thing.\nI wonder if I can properly convey how fun the game is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "緊張しているみたいだけど、すみれなら大丈夫だ\n歌もMCも沢山練習してきたんだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look nervous‚ but you'll be fine‚ Sumire.\nYou've practiced the songs and MCing a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 139.6666631658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですけど、みんなの前で披露するのは\n初めてなので、落ち着かなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ but since it's the first time\nperforming in front of everyone‚ I'm restless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。……そういえば、俺も魔法を使えるんだ\nいくぞ……大丈夫だシャイニー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. …Come to think of it‚ I can use magic too.\nHere I go… Shiny All Right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……え、えーっと……{user}さん……？\n魔法は出ないのが普通ですよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…U-Um… {user}…?\nI told you‚ it's normal for magic NOT to work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 163.2666631658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが緊張しなくなるようにと思ったんだが……\n慣れないことはするものじゃなかったか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just wanted to help you not feel nervous…\nMaybe I shouldn't try things I'm not used to…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ。確かに、もう緊張しなくなりました\n{user}さんは魔法使いだったんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hehe. It's true‚ I'm not nervous anymore.\nYou really were a wizard‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 178.6999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。お兄ちゃんの魔法のおかげで\nミニライブでも緊張せずに話せそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Thanks to Big Brother's magic‚\nI think I can speak at the mini-live without being nervous!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 185.5999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "しっかりと最後まで見守っているからな\n頑張れ、魔法少女ヴィオレット！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be watching over you until the very end.\nGood luck‚ Magical Girl Violette!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 192.0999964992
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
