      "text": "実は……今回、役作りに凄く悩んだんです\n自分らしい魔法少女ってなんだろう？　って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… I really struggled with character building this time.\nI wondered‚ \"What is a magical girl like me?\"…",
