      "text": "私は魔法が使える訳でも空が飛べる訳でもないから\n魔法少女の気持ちなんて分からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I can't use magic or fly in the sky‚\nI didn't understand the feelings of a magical girl at all…",
